      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|>It's just that there's no color left in anything. It feels like I'm just going through the motions, like a ghost in my own life. The grief is just so constant, and it's so exhausting to keep pretending that things will eventually get better when everything feels so empty. I just want the weight to stop. I just want to stop feeling like this.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
